        while (SDL_PollEvent(&event)) {
            if (event.type == SDL_QUIT) {
                SDL_Quit();
                exit(0);
            }
        }

        // Update game logic here

        SDL_SetRenderDrawColor(renderer, 0, 0, 0, 255);
        SDL_RenderClear(renderer);

        draw_snake(renderer, snake);
        draw_food(renderer, food);

        SDL_RenderPresent(renderer);
    }

    return 0;
}
```

This code sets up a basic window using SDL and loads two images for the snake and food. It then creates a game loop that updates the game logic and draws the snake and food on the screen.

